[Unlock All Dresses/Marionettes 	]
author=Pyriel
description=NOTE: The eleventh and final dress, available in the Japanese version, was removed by the company that localized the game. The reason given was difficulty in modifying the program to read the NTSC (US) save file. Apparently, the Japanese version of Covenant parsed that region's equivalent of a greatest hits save file from the first game. The original and greatest hits save were vastly different and since the US never saw a greatest hits version, everybody's save would be illegible to the game. It's up to you whether or not you believe that or choose to think it's the typical censorship that takes place in localizing games to the US. In either event: No puppet porn for you! 
patch=1,EE,1010106C,extended,0000FFFF
patch=1,EE,10103028,extended,0000FFFF
patch=1,EE,00000000,extended,00000000

